{"title_page": "Armed Forces of Ukraine", "text_new": "{{Infobox national military\n| name               = Armed Forces of Ukraine\n| native_name        = {{lang|uk|\u0417\u0431\u0440\u043e\u0439\u043d\u0456 \u0441\u0438\u043b\u0438 \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0457\u043d\u0438|italic=no}}\n| badge= Emblem of the Ukrainian Armed Forces.svg\n| badgecaption            = Emblem\n| flag = Ensign of the Ukrainian Armed Forces.svg\n| flagcaption           = Flag\n| motto              =\n| founded            = 1917\n| current_form       = 6 December 1991<ref>{{cite web|url=http://zakon1.rada.gov.ua/laws/show/1934-12|title=\u041f\u0440\u043e \u0417\u0431\u0440\u043e\u0439\u043d\u0456 \u0421\u0438\u043b\u0438 \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0457\u043d\u0438 - \u0432\u0456\u0434 6 December 1991 \u2116 1934-XII|website=zakon1.rada.gov.ua|access-date=1 June 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120330165053/http://zakon1.rada.gov.ua/laws/show/1934-12|archive-date=30 March 2012|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n| disbanded          =\n| branches           = {{nowrap|{{Army|Ukraine|name=Ground Forces}}}}<br />{{nowrap|{{Flagicon image|Ensign of the Ukrainian Air Force.svg|size=23px}} [[Ukrainian Air Force|Air Force]]}}<br />{{nowrap|{{Flagicon image|Naval Ensign of Ukraine.svg|size=23px}} [[Ukrainian Navy|Navy]]}}<br />{{nowrap|{{Flagicon image|\u041f\u0440\u0430\u043f\u043e\u0440 \u0414\u0428\u0412.svg|border=|size=25px}} [[Ukrainian Air Assault Forces|Air Assault Forces]]}}<br />{{nowrap|{{flagicon image|Flag of the Special Operations Forces of Ukraine.svg|size=23px}} [[Special Operations Forces (Ukraine)|Special Operations Forces]]}}<ref name=\"SF\">[http://espreso.tv/article/2015/04/22/komanduvannya_sso___novyy_rid_viysk Special Operations Forces, what will the new branch be like?] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150921030127/http://espreso.tv/article/2015/04/22/komanduvannya_sso___novyy_rid_viysk |date=2015-09-21 }}. ESPRESO. 22 April 2015</ref>\n| headquarters       = [[Ministry of Defence building (Ukraine)|Ministry of Defence Building]], Povitroflotskyi Square, [[Kiev]]\n| flying_hours       =\n| website            = <!--{{URL|example.mil}}-->\n<!-- Leadership -->\n| commander-in-chief = {{flagicon image|Flag of the President of Ukraine.svg}} [[Volodymyr Zelensky]]\n| commander-in-chief_title = [[President of Ukraine|Supreme Commander-in-Chief]]\n| chief minister     =\n| chief minister_title =\n| minister           = {{flagicon image|Standard of the Ukrainian Defense Minister rect.svg}} [[Andriy Taran]]<ref>[https://www.unian.info/m/politics/10902101-ukrainian-lawmakers-appoint-andriy-taran-as-new-defense-minister.html Ukrainian lawmakers appoint Andriy Taran as new defense minister], by [[UNIAN]]</ref> \n| minister_title     = [[List of Ministers of Defense (Ukraine)|Minister of Defence]]\n| commander          = {{flagicon image|Standard of Ukrainian Chief of the General Staff rect.svg}} [[Ruslan Khomchak]]<ref name=\"Serhiy Korniychuk CGSUbc\">[https://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/650657.html Zelensky appoints Khomchak Chief Commander of Armed Forces, Korniychuk Chief of General Staff], [[Interfax-Ukraine]] (28 March 2020)</ref>\n| commander_title    = [[Chief Commander of Armed Forces (Ukraine)|Chief Commander of Armed Forces]]<ref name=\"Serhiy Korniychuk CGSUbc\"/>\n<!-- Manpower -->\n| age                = 18<ref>\"''\u0421\u0442\u0430\u0442\u0442\u044f 15. \u041f\u0440\u0438\u0437\u043e\u0432\u043d\u0438\u0439 \u0432\u0456\u043a. \u041f\u0440\u0438\u0437\u043e\u0432 \u0433\u0440\u043e\u043c\u0430\u0434\u044f\u043d \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0457\u043d\u0438 \u043d\u0430 \u0441\u0442\u0440\u043e\u043a\u043e\u0432\u0443 \u0432\u0456\u0439\u0441\u044c\u043a\u043e\u0432\u0443 \u0441\u043b\u0443\u0436\u0431\u0443. \u041d\u0430 \u0441\u0442\u0440\u043e\u043a\u043e\u0432\u0443 \u0432\u0456\u0439\u0441\u044c\u043a\u043e\u0432\u0443 \u0441\u043b\u0443\u0436\u0431\u0443 \u0432 \u043c\u0438\u0440\u043d\u0438\u0439 \u